--- !u!114 &705910102
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 705910100}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: f4688fdb7df04437aeb418b961361dc5, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Unity.TextMeshPro::TMPro.TextMeshProUGUI
  m_Material: {fileID: 0}
  m_Color: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
  m_RaycastTarget: 1
  m_RaycastPadding: {x: 0, y: 0, z: 0, w: 0}
  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "1) Sim\xFClasyon alan\u0131nda ilerleyerek cerrahi aletlere yakla\u015F\u0131n.\n\n2)
    Bir aleti almak i\xE7in sa\u011F controller \xFCzerindeki Grip tu\u015Funa bir
    kere bas\u0131n.\n\n3) Ald\u0131\u011F\u0131n\u0131z aleti ta\u015F\u0131yarak
    do\u011Fru yuvas\u0131na g\xF6t\xFCr\xFCn.\n\n4) Do\u011Fru yuvaya yakla\u015Ft\u0131\u011F\u0131n\u0131zda
    hedef alan g\xF6rsel olarak vurgulan\u0131r.\n\n5) Aleti yuvaya b\u0131rakmak
    i\xE7in tekrar Grip tu\u015Funa bas\u0131n.\n\n6) Alet yanl\u0131\u015F yuvaya
    b\u0131rak\u0131l\u0131rsa kabul edilmez.\n\n7) Do\u011Fru yuvaya yerle\u015Ftirilen
    alet kilitlenir ve tekrar al\u0131namaz.\n\n8) T\xFCm aletler do\u011Fru yuvalara
    yerle\u015Ftirildi\u011Finde sim\xFClasyon tamamlan\u0131r.\n\n9) Durdurma men\xFCs\xFCn\xFC
    a\xE7mak i\xE7in sa\u011F controller \xFCzerindeki B tu\u015Funa bas\u0131n.\n\n10)
    Men\xFC \xFCzerindeki butonlar\u0131 se\xE7mek ve t\u0131klamak i\xE7in sa\u011F
    controller\u0131n i\u015Faretleme sistemiyle hedef al\u0131n ve R1 tu\u015Funu
    kullan\u0131n."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 2180264, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
